    <item>
      <title>印度即将批准投资 Paytm 有望小胜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-09/paytm-set-for-small-win-as-india-close-to-approving-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Paytm 即将获得印度批准投资其主要支付网关部门，这一决定已经等待了两年，这将给这家陷入困境的金融科技公司带来一些喘息的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-09/paytm-set-for-small-win-as-india-close-to-approving-investment</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 10:09:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本拨款 3 亿美元启动国内芯片研究</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-09/japan-shores-up-research-push-to-catch-up-on-advanced-chip-tech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本将斥资高达 450 亿日元（约合 3 亿美元）来支持一个开发先进芯片技术的研究小组，这是国家追赶半导体制造业的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-09/japan-shores-up-research-push-to-catch-up-on-advanced-chip-tech</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 01:30:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
